&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;10+ years of enterprise SaaS sales experience managing and closing complex deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success closing $1M+ ACV enterprise SaaS transactions&lt;/li&

